# GHCJS - The Haskell to JavaScript Compiler

## Installation

### Install Prerequisite

    sudo apt-get install libtinfo-dev

This installs directly into my local binary directory /home/roland/bin

### Prepare $PATH .profile

    # set PATH so it includes user's private bin if it exists
    if [ -d "$HOME/Software/ghcjs/bin" ] ; then
        PATH="$HOME/Software/ghcjs/bin:$PATH"
    fi

### Install ghcjs

For GHCJS there is only one version active.

~~~
cd ~/Software
mkdir ghcjs
cd ghcjs
mkdir bin
cabal sandbox init
cabal install --bindir=/home/roland/Software/ghcjs/bin http://ghcjs.luite.com/master.tar.gz
ghcjs-boot
~~~

